N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4401.1 - Form of commission decision, directive or order

State Regulations
A decision, order or directive of the commission shall be
issued over the signature of the executive director of the commission, the
secretary to the commission, or over the signature of the designee of the
executive director. Notes
